languages.text: В трещине едва видны темные перекрученные фигуры — замерзшие люди.
You can just barely see dark, twisted silhouettes through the crack: these people froze to death.

languages.text: 透过裂缝，你只能勉强看到黑暗之中扭曲的身影，这些人都是被冻死的。
languages.original_text: You can just barely see dark, twisted silhouettes through the crack: these people froze to death.

languages.text: Du kannst durch den Riss gerade so dunkle, unnatürlich verdrehte Silhouetten ausmachen. Diese Leute sind erfroren.
languages.original_text: You can just barely see dark, twisted silhouettes through the crack: these people froze to death.

traits.locale_text: Du kannst durch den Riss mit Mühe dunklen, unnatürlich verdrehte Silhouetten ausmachen. Diese Leute sind erfroren.

languages.text: A través de la grieta vislumbras a duras penas unas siluetas oscuras y retorcidas: esta gente murió congelada.
languages.original_text: You can just barely see dark, twisted silhouettes through the crack: these people froze to death.

traits.locale_text: A través de la grieta vislumbras a duras penas unas siluetas oscuras y retorcidas: esta gente murió congelada.

languages.text: Par la fissure, vous distinguez à peine de sombres silhouettes tordues : ces morts ont succombé au froid.
languages.original_text: You can just barely see dark, twisted silhouettes through the crack: these people froze to death.

traits.locale_text: Par la fissure, vous distinguez à peine de sombres silhouettes tordues : ces morts ont succombé au froid.

languages.text: その裂け目から、黒く歪んだシルエットがかろうじて見える。彼らは凍え死んだのだ。
languages.original_text: You can just barely see dark, twisted silhouettes through the crack: these people froze to death.

traits.locale_text: その裂け目から、黒く歪んだシルエットがかろうじて見える。彼らは凍え死んだのだ。

languages.text: Yarıktan çıkan çarpılmış silüetleri karanlıkta zar zor seçebiliyorsun. Bu varlıklar donarak ölmüş.
